               effect include: the refraction of neutrinos in matter, the
               resonance (level crossing) and the adiabaticity. The key notion
               is \{\textbackslashit the neutrino eigenstates\} in matter.
               Physical picture of the effect is described in terms of the
               flavors and the relative phases of eigenstates and the
               transitions between eigenstates. Features of the large mixing
               realization of the MSW effect are discussed. The large mixing
               MSW effect (LMA) provides the solution of the solar neutrino
               problem. We show in details how this mechanism works. Physics
               beyond the LMA solution is discussed. The lower $Ar$-production
